{"tid":412393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中甲球隊遭保安闖更衣室毆打4傷 下半場「失蹤」","createTime":"2017-09-24T15:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T05:17:03.000Z","uid":109743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfd70220045f70bc0783b6ca54159daaf6b7a7d","tid":412393,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"2017賽季中甲第27輪比賽昨日舉行，雲南麗江飛虎在主場迎戰浙江毅騰。據悉，半場比賽過後，浙江毅騰因為對主裁判的判罰不滿拒絕出戰下半場比賽。隨後更是有現場球迷爆料稱，毅騰一名球員遭麗江主場保安人員及疑似特警人員打傷。球隊下半場比賽拒回到場內比賽，不過經過協調，雙方耽擱了40分鐘之後重新登場。隨後浙江毅騰俱樂部把投訴被打的微博刪除。據指毅騰球員事後入院檢查，證實至少有4人分別是「頭部外傷」或「顱腦外傷」。麗江飛虎則稱：「堅決支持賽區安保部門維護賽場秩序。」目前，中國足協已介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n賽前，麗江飛虎累積20分排名中甲最後一位，而浙江毅騰積25分排名第13位，這對雙方而言都是輸不起的比賽。上半場比賽，浙江毅騰由艾爾帕提-迪力夏率先破門，隨後麗江飛虎在半場結束前通過一粒有爭議的球扳平了比分，這讓毅騰方面非常不滿。另外，主裁判還有另外兩次判罰也備受爭議。<br />\n中場休息過後，毅騰球員遲遲未回到賽場。下半場比賽本過了30分鐘都沒人出場。<br />\n網友爆料艾爾帕提被保安、特警打傷，隨後，據現場球迷爆料稱，中場休息時，浙江毅騰上半場進球的球員艾爾帕提-迪力夏同主場的保安起了衝突，保安闖入更衣室打人，這才導致毅騰方面拒絕出戰下半場比賽。<br />\n另據賽事旁述稱，衝突的經過是：「毅騰不滿判罰先圍堵裁判，繼而同現場保安發生衝突，艾爾帕提在衝突中被保安打傷。」具體是怎樣的情況，有待官方的正式通報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170924/57248633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170924%2F57248633&d=XSbuDkYM8s2eWeda%2FQGdIGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7aa11b9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170924%2F57248633&h=6e4eb8bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170924/57248633</a>"},{"pid":"84ba80844b4e1329ad8fee693867024b6eec10b8","tid":412393,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/36166_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F36166_WM.jpg&h=d41adb0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e73ba2b58db15fd5e9b891b0537ba82666b0763","tid":412393,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/f683c17bc88f4f9d8d6ea29de086954a20170923185802.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2Ff683c17bc88f4f9d8d6ea29de086954a20170923185802.gif&h=5942d4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似真係拉底左喎"},{"pid":"3da9761216eba9676d05da479aa3066dc623ca78","tid":412393,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"efb6a6bd8aea44b9b098a4b393fbba2d1a50c282","tid":412393,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/f683c17bc88f4f9d8d6ea29de086954a20170923185802.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2Ff683c17bc88f4f9d8d6ea29de086954a20170923185802.gif&h=5942d4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似真係拉底左喎</blockquote><br />\n有拉，但睇落主因係藍衫飛剷，唔係比人拉低，果下唔剷既話個波就係彈向另邊白衫果到，藍衫更加無機會hi到粒波"},{"pid":"183b235a813c90764f2f135fd4957af2b8c2ca2d","tid":412393,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c733090eff8f327a7088b974ba5da82805a447e4","tid":412393,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f768fc8d9f7a7177f9c8b1dfdfe93c41fd89e96e","tid":412393,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9337b09ea7c5a4ff987ce128c51aaabdb94d758","tid":412393,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,